#. Tag: title
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Description</title>"
msgstr "<title>Opis</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open Document Text report templates are regular ODT files that can be "
"designed using any ODT word processor like <emphasis>Calligra Words</"
"emphasis> or <emphasis>LibreOffice Writer</emphasis>. The technique used is "
"to use <emphasis>user field</emphasis> variables to hold references to the "
"information that shall be fetched from the project. The variables are called "
"<emphasis>User Fields</emphasis> in <emphasis>Writer</emphasis> and can be "
"found under <menuchoice><guimenu>Insert</guimenu><guisubmenu>Field</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>More Fields</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Variables</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>User Fields</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. In "
"<emphasis>Words</emphasis> they are called <emphasis>Custom Variables</"
"emphasis> and can be found under <menuchoice><guimenu>Text Editing docker</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Variable</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Custom</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Predloge odprtih besedilnih dokumentov poročil so običajne datoteke ODT, ki "
"jih je mogoče oblikovati s katerim koli urejevalnikom besedil ODT, kot je "
"<emphasis>Calligra Words</emphasis> ali <emphasis>LibreOffice Writer</"
"emphasis>. Uporabljena tehnika je uporaba spremenljivk "
"<emphasis>uporabniškega polja</emphasis> za shranjevanje sklicev na "
"informacije, ki bodo pridobljene iz projekta. Spremenljivke se imenujejo "
"<emphasis>Uporabniška polja</emphasis> v programu <emphasis>Writer</"
"emphasis> in jih najdete pod <menuchoice><guimenu>Vstavi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Polje</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Več polj</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Spremenljivke</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Uporabniška "
"polja</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. V <emphasis>Words</emphasis> se imenujejo "
"<emphasis>Spremenljivke po meri</emphasis> in jih najdete pod "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sidrišče za urejanje besedila</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Spremenljivka</guisubmenu><guimenuitem> Po meri</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The easiest way to create a new report template is to modify an existing one "
"as all user fields are defined."
msgstr ""
"Novo predlogo poročila najlažje ustvarite tako, da spremenite obstoječo, saj "
"so definirana vsa uporabniška polja."

#. Tag: title
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "User Field Variables"
msgstr "Spremenljivke uporabniških polj"

#. Tag: title
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "Variables"
msgstr "Spremenljivke"

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The variables are used to enable the generator to extract data from the "
"project."
msgstr ""
"Spremenljivke se uporabljajo, da generatorju omogočijo pridobivanje podatkov "
"iz projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A variable can be a reference to a single data field, a reference to table "
"data or a reference to chart data."
msgstr ""
"Spremenljivka je lahko sklic na posamezno podatkovno polje, sklic na podatke "
"tabele ali sklic na podatke grafikona."

#. Tag: sect4
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<sect5><title>Single Data Field</title> <para>A single data field variable "
"has the following format: </para> <para><replaceable>data group name</"
"replaceable>.<replaceable>property</replaceable> = <replaceable>property "
"identifier</replaceable> </para> <para>where: </para> <itemizedlist> "
"<listitem><para><replaceable>data group name</replaceable> can be tr, "
"project or schedule (see below).</para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para><replaceable>property</replaceable> makes the user field "
"name unique.</para></listitem> <listitem><para><replaceable>property "
"identity</replaceable> identifies the property in the data group.</para></"
"listitem> </itemizedlist> </sect5> <sect5><title>Table Data</title> <para>A "
"table in a report template consists of a variable to specify the data table "
"to use. </para> <para>The variable name must start with <replaceable>table</"
"replaceable> (&eg; tableTasks) and the variable value must be the name of "
"the data table (&eg; tasks). </para> <para>Immediately after the variable, a "
"table must be inserted and columns filled with user field variables that "
"specify which properties to fetch from the table specified above. These "
"variables must have names that start with the name of the table variable "
"above. </para> <para>These variables have the following format: </para> "
"<para>tableTasks.<replaceable>property</replaceable> = <replaceable>property "
"identifier</replaceable> </para> <para>where: </para> <itemizedlist> "
"<listitem><para><guilabel>property</guilabel> makes the user field name "
"unique.</para></listitem> <listitem><para><guilabel>property identifier</"
"guilabel> identifies the property in the data group.</para></listitem> </"
"itemizedlist> </sect5> <sect5><title>Chart Data</title> <para>A chart in a "
"report template consists of a variable to specify the data to use in the "
"chart. </para> <para>The variable name must start with <replaceable>chart</"
"replaceable> (&eg; chartBudgetCost) and the variable value specifies the "
"data group and values to populate the chart. </para> <para>The variable has "
"the following format (note the semicolons): </para> <para><replaceable>name</"
"replaceable> = <replaceable>data group</replaceable>; "
"values=<replaceable>comma separated list of data properties</replaceable>; </"
"para> <para>where: </para> <itemizedlist> <listitem><para><replaceable>name</"
"replaceable> must start with <guilabel>chart</guilabel> (&eg; "
"chartBudgetCost)</para></listitem> <listitem><para><replaceable>data group</"
"replaceable></para></listitem> <listitem><para><guilabel>comma separated "
"list of data properties</guilabel> identifies the properties in the data "
"group.</para></listitem> </itemizedlist> <para>E.g.: </para> "
"<para>chartBudget = project; values=bcws cost, bcwp cost, acwp cost; </para> "
"</sect5>"
msgstr ""
"<sect5><title>Eno podatkovno polje</title> <para>Ena spremenljivka "
"podatkovnega polja ima naslednjo obliko: </para> <para><replaceable>ime "
"podatkovne skupine</replaceable>.<replaceable>lastnost</replaceable> = "
"<replaceable>identifikator lastnosti</replaceable> </para> <para>kjer je: </"
"para> <itemizedlist> <listitem><para><replaceable>ime podatkovne skupine</"
"replaceable> je lahko tr, project ali razpored (glejte spodaj).</para></"
"listitem> <listitem><para><replaceable>lastnost</replaceable> naredi ime "
"uporabniškega polja edinstveno.</para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para><replaceable>identiteta lastnosti</replaceable> identificira "
"lastnost v skupini podatkov.</para></listitem> </itemizedlist> </sect5> "
"<sect5><title>Podatki tabele</title> <para>Tabela v Predloga poročila je "
"sestavljena iz spremenljivke za določanje podatkovne tabele za uporabo. </"
"para> <para >Ime spremenljivke se mora začeti s <replaceable>table</"
"replaceable> (&eg; tableTasks) in vrednost spremenljivke mora biti ime "
"podatkovne tabele (&eg; tasks). </para> <para >Takoj za spremenljivko je "
"treba vstaviti tabelo in stolpce izpolniti s spremenljivkami uporabniškega "
"polja, ki določajo, katere lastnosti je treba pridobiti iz zgoraj navedene "
"tabele. Te spremenljivke morajo imeti imena, ki se začnejo z imenom "
"spremenljivke zgornje tabele. </para> <para>Te spremenljivke imajo naslednjo "
"obliko: </para> <para>tableTasks.<replaceable>lastnost</replaceable> = "
"<replaceable>identifikator lastnosti</replaceable> </para> <para>kjer je: </"
"para> <itemizedlist> <listitem><para><guilabel>lastnost</guilabel> naredi "
"ime uporabniškega polja edinstveno.</para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para><guilabel>identifikator lastnosti</guilabel > identificira "
"lastnost v skupini podatkov.</para></listitem> </itemizedlist> </sect5> "
"<sect5><title>Podatki grafikona</title> <para>Grafikon v predlogi poročila "
"je sestavljen iz spremenljivke da določite podatke za uporabo v grafikonu. </"
"para> <para >Ime spremenljivke se mora začeti z <replaceable>chart</"
"replaceable> (&eg; chartBudgetCost), vrednost spremenljivke pa določa "
"podatkovno skupino in vrednosti za zapolnitev grafikona. </para> <para "
">Spremenljivka ima naslednjo obliko (upoštevajte podpičja): </para> "
"<para><replaceable>ime</replaceable> = <replaceable>skupina podatkov</"
"replaceable>; values=<replaceable>z vejicami ločen seznam lastnosti "
"podatkov</replaceable>; </para> <para>kjer: </para> <itemizedlist> "
"<listitem><para><replaceable>ime</replaceable> se mora začeti z "
"<guilabel>chart</guilabel> (&eg; chartBudgetCost)</para> </listitem> "
"<listitem><para><replaceable>podatkovna skupina</replaceable></para></"
"listitem> <listitem><para><guilabel>z vejicami ločen seznam lastnosti "
"podatkov</guilabel> identificira lastnosti v skupino podatkov.</para></"
"listitem> </itemizedlist> <para>&eg; </para> <para>chartBudget = projekt; "
"vrednosti=bcws cost, bcwp cost, acwp cost; </para> </sect5>"

