#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a table, place a variable just before a table in your template "
"file. The variable name identifies the table and must start with "
"<guilabel>table</guilabel>, &eg; <guilabel>tableTaskStatus</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti tabelo, postavite spremenljivko tik pred tabelo v "
"datoteki predloge. Ime spremenljivke identificira tabelo in se mora začeti z "
"<guilabel>table</guilabel>, &eg; <guilabel>tableTaskStatus</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The value of the variable is used to point to the data to be fetched and "
"must be one of the supported tables listed above, &eg; <guilabel>taskstatus</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Vrednost spremenljivke se uporablja za kazanje na podatke, ki jih je treba "
"pridobiti, in mora biti ena od podprtih tabel, navedenih zgoraj, &eg; "
"<guilabel>stanje naloge</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You then put variables inside the table cells with name and value from the "
"table below."
msgstr ""
"Nato v celice tabele vstavite spremenljivke z imenom in vrednostjo iz "
"spodnje tabele."

#. Tag: para
#: creatingodtreporttemplates.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that the schedules table supports the values described in <link linkend="
"\"schedule-values\">Schedule Values</link> above."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da tabela razporedov podpira vrednosti, opisane v <link linkend="
"\"schedule-values\">Vrednosti razporeda</link> zgoraj."

